&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;The role is a great opportunity for someone who is keen to be part of a global cryptocurrency business. The country Marketing Manager will look to lead and drive all Luno marketing activities across multiple channels.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
